name: Introduction to C Programming
details: Learn the basics of C programming in this introductory course. Covers syntax, data types, and control structures.

name: Introduction to Algorithms
details: Explore fundamental algorithms and problem-solving techniques. Topics include sorting, searching, and complexity analysis.

name: Introduction to C++ for DSA
details: Start your journey in C++ for Data Structures and Algorithms. Covers pointers, classes, and basic data structures.

name: Basic Data Structures
details: Master essential data structures like arrays, linked lists, and stacks. Practical implementation and usage are emphasized.

name: Introduction to OOP Python
details: Delve into object-oriented programming with Python. Learn classes, inheritance, and encapsulation through real-world examples.

name: Software Engineering
details: Discover software engineering principles. Covers requirements, design, testing, and project management in software development.

name: AWS Cloud Computing
details: Learn cloud computing with AWS. Topics include EC2, S3, and networking. Hands-on labs for practical experience.

name: Database (MySQL)
details: Master MySQL for database management. Covers SQL, database design, and administration for real-world applications.

name: Problem-Solving Part
details: Enhance your problem-solving skills with practical exercises. Learn algorithmic techniques to tackle complex problems.
